changelog:
This Update is a fun one: Fixed Memory Leak ( as previously tested in 4.45x ) 
Added Support for Custom Banlists ( e.g. MySQL ), see https://github.com/Bluethefurry/EasyAdmin/wiki/7.-Custom-Banlist-Plugins
Add a 'convertbanlist' command for the previously mentioned feature
Added Polish Translation
Fixed some buttons in the Settings Menu not doing anything when pressed
